## Partitioning Data

  # Dividing data into training and testing sets using a 70/30 split
  # Random sampling 
    samplesize = 0.70*nrow(data)
    set.seed(100)
    index = sample(seq_len(nrow(data)), size = samplesize)

    test = data[-index,]
